#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/nightmare.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Armor Class** 13 (natural armor)    \n"
"**Hit Points** 68 (8d10 + 24)    \n"
"**Speed** 60 ft., fly 90 ft. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/nightmare.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| STR     | DEX     | CON     | INT     | WIS     | CHA     |\n"
"|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|---------|\n"
"| 18 (+4) | 15 (+2) | 16 (+3) | 10 (+0) | 13 (+1) | 15 (+2) |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/nightmare.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Damage Immunities** fire    \n"
"**Senses** passive Perception 11    \n"
"**Languages** understands Abyssal, Common, and Infernal but can't speak    "
"\n"
"**Challenge** 3 (700 XP) \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/nightmare.md:23
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Confer Fire Resistance.** The nightmare can grant resistance to fire "
"damage to anyone riding it.    \n"
"**Illumination.** The nightmare sheds bright light in a 10-foot radius and "
"dim light for an additional 10 feet. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/monsters/nightmare.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"### Actions \n"
"**Hooves.** _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +6 to hit, reach 5 ft., one "
"target. _Hit:_ 13 (2d8 + 4) bludgeoning damage plus 7 (2d6) fire damage.    "
"\n"
"**Ethereal Stride.** The nightmare and up to three willing creatures within "
"5 feet of it magically enter the Ethereal Plane from the Material Plane, or "
"vice versa.\n"
msgstr ""
